    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A very minimalistic TCG auto-battler featuring creatures called Fomons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your collection: Find a new Fomon every hours. <strong>NOT DURING DEMO PLAY</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the perfect specimen: Each Fomon comes with a Tier and unique attributes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a Fomon from your collection and let it fight for you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with others climbing the Leaderboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge duplicate Fomon into stronger Tiers.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Note: Some mentioned features are still roadmap material.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166930/extras/0ab310957972935ff0d30f69d5d3f645.avif?t=1741185374\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166930/extras_big/0ab310957972935ff0d30f69d5d3f645.avif?t=1741185374 width=800 height=1406 /></span></p>",
